					<h2>James Raussen</h2>				
					<h5>AAPSCM® Executive Trainer, Key Speaker &amp; Strategic Advisor</h5>				
		<p>James Raussen is a distinguished Executive Trainer and Global Strategic Advisor with the American Association of Procurement &amp; Supply Chain Management (AAPSCM®). With a dynamic career that bridges public leadership and private-sector transformation, James brings over two decades of expertise in government innovation, international consulting, fiscal strategy, and executive development.</p><p>James Raussen continues to be a sought-after voice in public-private collaboration, policy transformation, and supply chain governance, bringing exceptional value to AAPSCM’s global training network.</p>
